{"WABBLE":[{"def":"To move staggeringly or unsteadily from one side to the other; to vacillate; to move the manner of a rotating disk when the axis of rotation is inclined to that of the disk; -- said of a turning or whirling body; as, a top wabbles; a buzz saw wabbles.","pos":""}],"WABBLY":[{"def":"Inclined to wabble; wabbling.","pos":""},{"def":"A soft, earthy, dark-colored rock or clay derived from the alteration of basalt.","pos":""}]}